            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11558125">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">第一章第一段

他是当时德国为数很少的信仰社会主义的大学教师之一，作为一名极左派，他对他的大学同事颇为厌烦。

 One of the few German socialist academics, he was frowned upon by his university colleagues as an extreme leftist.

 他是被同事们厌烦


 </span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11558125/">(<span class="">3回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-02-26 04:26</span>
                  
